These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: comedy, disaster, fantasy, horror, satire, scientific, superhero
There are 7 different nationalities: thai, australian, canadian, indonesian, malaysian, nigerian, polish
City: hannover, marseilles, edinburgh, new-york, boston, paris, venice
 1. the person watching satire movies is on the far left##1
 2. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
 3. the person traveling to venice is between the australian and the thai##2
 4. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
 5. the australian is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 6. the person watching comedy movies is the person traveling to venice##1
 7. the indonesian is between the person traveling to new-york and the person watching satire movies##2
 8. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
 9. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
10. the person watching superhero movies is the canadian##1
11. the nigerian is the person watching horror movies##1
12. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
13. the person traveling to hannover is the malaysian##1
14. the person watching scientific movies is between the person traveling to edinburgh and the person traveling to venice##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |    7     |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | comedy     | scientific | disaster | horror | superhero  | fantasy  |
| Nationality   | thai  | indonesian        | australian  | polish     | nigerian   | canadian       | malaysian   |
| City         | marseilles   | venice | new-york    | edinburgh  | boston | paris | hannover |

