.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-2::.
There are 7 different nationalities: british, canadian, colombian, egyptian, indian, japanese, thai
7 different pets are kept: hedgehog, rat, ferret, dog, guinea-pig, frog, hamster
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: january, july, april, august, october, may, march
 1. the canadian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 2. the owner of the guinea-pig is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 4. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 5. the owner of the hedgehog is the thai##1
 6. the british is the person who's birthday is in august##1
 7. the british is between the owner of the hamster and the person who's birthday is in march##2
 8. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the indian##1
 9. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
10. the colombian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
11. the indian is on the right of the british##1
12. the person who's birthday is in january is the canadian##1
13. the egyptian is on the left of the british##1
14. the egyptian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
15. the canadian is on the far right##1
16. the owner of the rat is on the left of the thai##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3       |    4     |   5    |     6     |    7     |
| Nationality   | japanese | thai      | egyptian     | british  | indian | colombian | canadian |
| Pet         | rat  | hedgehog | frog | ferret | hamster | dog   | guinea-pig  |
| Birthday     | april   | may     | march        | august  | october   | july       | january      |

