 2. the person eating papaya is the journalist##1
 3. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the manager##1
 4. the person eating radish is the person who's birthday is in august##1
 5. the person eating corn is between the person eating cucumber and the photographer##2
 6. the person eating papaya is on the right of the person eating mango##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 8. the person eating radish is on the left of the photographer##1
 9. the person eating cucumber is on the far right##1
10. the engineer is on the right of the musician##1
11. the person eating nectarine is the accountant##1
12. the engineer is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
13. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the journalist##1
14. the person eating cucumber is the person who's birthday is in january##1
15. the person eating mango is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1

