.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-4::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: baking, collecting, cooking, filmmaking, woodworking, camping, chess
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: action, adventure, animation, drama, musical, scientific, zombie
The people use 7 different means of transport: taxi, jet-ski, bus, subway, quad-bike, ship, snowmobile
 1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left##1
 2. the person watching scientific movies is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 3. the person driving the bus is the person watching drama movies##1
 4. the person watching adventure movies is on the far right##1
 5. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 6. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
 7. the person who's hobby is baking is in the middle##1
 8. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the person driving the ship is the person watching action movies##1
10. the person driving the taxi is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
11. the person watching animation movies is the person driving the snowmobile##1
12. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person driving the quad-bike##1
13. the person driving the subway is on the far right##1
14. the person watching zombie movies is between the person watching animation movies and the person watching drama movies##2
15. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |    3     |    4    |     5      |     6      |     7     |
| Hobby          | collecting  | camping    | woodworking  | baking | filmmaking  | chess | cooking |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | animation | zombie   | drama   | scientific | action     | adventure |
| Transport   | quad-bike | snowmobile   | taxi | bus  | jet-ski   | ship    | subway    |

