.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-5::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  analyst, architect, doctor, firefighter, freelancer, journalist, writer
There are 7 different favourite colors: chestnut, black, ebony, yellow, apricot, coral, turquise
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: daisy, zinnia, orchid, tulip, iris, daffodil, rose
 1. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the writer##1
 2. the freelancer is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 3. the freelancer is the person who likes black##1
 4. the firefighter is the person who growstulip##1
 5. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
 6. the person who likes chestnut is the journalist##1
 7. the analyst is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
 8. the person who growszinnia is the doctor##1
 9. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
10. the person who growsdaffodil is the person who likes chestnut##1
11. the doctor is on the right of the firefighter##1
12. the person who growsiris is between the doctor and the analyst##2
13. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the doctor##1
14. the person who growsdaisy is the person who likes apricot##1
15. the freelancer is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
16. the person who growstulip is the person who likes yellow##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |     5      |     6      |     7     |
| Job           | firefighter | doctor    | writer    | analyst  | freelancer | journalist | architect |
| Color   | yellow      | turquise | ebony | coral | black    | chestnut | apricot    |
| Flower     | tulip     | zinnia      | iris    | rose    | orchid  | daffodil       | daisy  |

