7 different pets are kept: cat, frog, hedgehog, lizard, mouse, pony, rabbit
 1. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 2. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 3. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
 4. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 5. the person who's hobby is collecting is the owner of the mouse##1
 6. the owner of the cat is between the person who's hobby is gardening and the person who's hobby is writing##2
 7. the person who's hobby is camping is in the middle##1
 8. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
 9. the owner of the pony is the person traveling to nizza##1
10. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
11. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the owner of the hedgehog##1
12. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the owner of the hedgehog##1
13. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
14. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
15. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
