The people have 7 different jobs:  lawyer, manager, social-worker, mechanic, scientist, paramedic, teacher
The people use 7 different means of transport: bus, car, roller, skateboard, taxi, train, tram
 1. the game-smoker is on the far right##1
 2. the person driving the roller is in the middle##1
 3. the paramedic is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
 4. the alhambra-smoker is between the blend-smoker and the siglo-smoker##2
 5. the lawyer is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 6. the davidoff-smoker is the teacher##1
 7. the blend-smoker is the person driving the train##1
 8. the social-worker is on the left of the manager##1
 9. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the person driving the car##1
10. the person driving the roller is on the right of the paramedic##1
11. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the train##1
12. the lawyer is in the middle##1
13. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
14. the person driving the skateboard is the mechanic##1
15. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the mechanic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |     5      |     6     |     7      |
| Cigar        | cain          | davidoff | blend      | alhambra  | siglo     | montecristo  | game |
