7 different pets are kept: bird, ferret, frog, guinea-pig, lizard, pony, rabbit
There 7 different types of food: banana, artichoke, pumpkin, papaya, broccoli, apple, corn
 1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
 2. the owner of the lizard is between the person drinking tea and the owner of the guinea-pig##2
 3. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
 4. the owner of the pony is on the far left##1
 5. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
 6. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 7. the person drinking lemonade is between the person eating banana and the owner of the lizard##2
 8. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
 9. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
10. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
11. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
12. the person drinking milk is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
13. the owner of the pony is the person eating apple##1
14. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
15. the person eating corn is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
16. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
