.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-16::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  coach, dancer, fisherman, manager, musician, photographer, writer
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: golf, lacrosse, sailing, biathlon, weightlifting, skiing, ice-hockey
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: zombie, horror, fantasy, time-travel, action, musical, epic
 1. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the fisherman##1
 2. the person watching musical movies is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person who's sport is sailing##2
 3. the person who's sport is golf is the person watching horror movies##1
 4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the photographer##1
 5. the person who's sport is golf is the coach##1
 6. the fisherman is in the middle##1
 7. the musician is the person who's sport is skiing##1
 8. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
 9. the person who's sport is golf is the person watching horror movies##1
10. the writer is the person watching action movies##1
11. the coach is on the right of the manager##1
12. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the photographer##1
13. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
14. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the coach##1
15. the writer is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2       |    3     |     4      |    5     |    6    |     7      |
| Job           | dancer | photographer | musician | fisherman  | writer   | manager | coach      |
| Sport   | ice-hockey | sailing        | skiing    | weightlifting     | biathlon     | lacrosse   | golf        |
| Movie-Genre           | zombie   | fantasy       | musical    | time-travel | action | epic   | horror |

