7 different pets are kept: cat, ferret, frog, goldfish, guinea-pig, lizard, snake
 1. the british is on the right of the colombian##1
 2. the owner of the lizard is in the middle##1
 3. the japanese is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 4. the thai is the person driving the airplane##1
 5. the person driving the trike is on the far right##1
 6. the owner of the lizard is the colombian##1
 7. the owner of the frog is the person driving the trike##1
 8. the owner of the goldfish is between the person driving the train and the owner of the frog##2
 9. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
10. the person driving the jet-ski is in the middle##1
11. the indian is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
12. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
13. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the chinese##1
14. the person driving the car is between the owner of the snake and the person driving the ship##2
15. the owner of the snake is the thai##1

.:: Answer ::.
